Located in Tilley Lane, Frenchs Forest on the southern side of Warringah Road, CBRE offer for lease is a small fitted out office fitted out suite.

The available suite is located on level 1 of a boutique office building called Aurora. The available suite is located on the Eastern side of the building, overlooking Tilley Lane.

The suite benefits from the following:
- Blinds to all windows
- Workstations and cabled throughout
- Excellent natural light flooding the suite
- Gross rental offering (No GST)
- Mix of external and basement parking
- Well know ground expresso café a stone’s throw away
- Walking distance to Warringah Aquatic Centre

Available for immediate occupation, contact Exclusive leasing agent CBRE; Tristan Winter or Ben Byford

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Situated on the Northern side of Rodborough Rd in the heart of Frenchs Forest. The property is within close proximity to Warringah Rd, providing quick access to the surrounding precincts and major arterial roads. The location is within 18kms from the CBD and 1.8kms away from The Northern Beaches Hospital.

The available unit is located on the upper level of Building A, 14 Rodborough Rd and enjoys a corner position with three sides of natural light and bright NE aspect.

The available unit benefits from:

+ Modern self-contained Hi-Tech unit
+ Perfect for office and technical users
+ Level 1 is currently fitted with perimeter offices, boardroom and open plan workspace.
+ Ground floor technical space is air conditioned, perfect for pick and pack or low clearance warehousing 
+ Available Jan 2021

For further details please contact exclusive leasing agents CBRE:
Ben Byford 0414 722 935

Warringah Corporate Centre is located on the Eastern end of Rodborough Road, approximately 18kms from the GPO. The location enjoys an elevated position with panoramic city and ocean views. It is also within close proximity to major shopping centres, public transport, cafes and Virgin Active gym.
  
Having recently undergone major refurbishments including new energy efficient lighting, passenger lifts and amenities. This ultra-modern 5 storey high-tech commercial building is suitable for office accommodation. 

The property has a striking glazed facade, situated in a business park environment with manicured landscaping. The stunning CBD quality foyer provides access to high speed lifts which also link the 3 levels of abundant security under cover car parking. An alfresco cafe, gymnasium and common lawn areas, BBQ entertaining complete this perfect corporate office facility.
